Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Tsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Nagumo, gajimu naik tiga kali lipat!\N- Sungguh mujur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengapa kau lakukan semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kami adalah restoran bintang satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pikirkan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senangnya!
