Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Begitu caranya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Begitu caranya?\N- Begitukah caramu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan orang-orang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia, Tatewaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus mengumpulkan energimu!
